@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@username = admin
@password = P@ssw0rd!

### 登录
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 查询登录日志
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/login-logs?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20&username=admin
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 导出登录日志
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/login-logs/export?username=admin&loginStatus=true
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 缺少令牌（预期 401）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/login-logs?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
